metadata.description:
If you want to show your eternal devotion for the Socerroos while also acknowledging their good fortune in this year's World Cup, then our Lucky Charm NFT Aidan Lee is here to cheer for them.

Collect these "Fans from other world" Lucky Charm NFTs to gain access to Fanisko Metaverse and NFT gaming with lot of utilities in future. These collectible NFTs will give you access to : 
- Enjoy your NFTs in Augmented Reality (AR) in Fanisko Metaverse App 
- Special powers to your gaming NFTs 
- Create your own private leagues in the metaverse 
- Get early bird access to all of the top-tier NFT airdrops, partner mints
